title: Flipping Out S09E10 The End Is Nigh WEB-DL x264-JIVE
description: Desperate to make progress on construction at his house, Jeff decides to cram the entire kitchen into his office. But as heat rises and tension mounts, Jeff and Gage find themselves in a power struggle before leaving town to meet up with Alexandra. As they take the final steps in prepping for the babys arrival, he works to wrap up as many client projects as possible. This is a bittersweet process for Jeff, as it means Zoila moves out to make room for the soon-to-be nursery
